## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Start the FastAPI server (`uvicorn main:app --reload`).
- Test `/api/scrape` with a sample URL via Swagger UI (`/docs`).
- Test `/api/upload` by uploading a PDF file.
- Test `/api/chat` to ensure the local LLM logic provides appropriate responses regarding RAG configuration.
- Trigger the frontend creation flow and verify it successfully hits the `/api/deploy` endpoint to initialize the RAG.
